Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.83,0:00:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,唐宁街里仍未有任何消息传出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's still no word from inside Downing Street. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.66,0:00:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但是更多政要接二连三走进首相府\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Though we are getting even more new arrivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是斯利辛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We are the Slitheen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把地球先熔成渣 再卖掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Reduce the Earth to molten slag, then sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.74,0:00:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,离开这颗行星 否则我会阻止你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Leave this planet or I'll stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.01,0:00:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,世界交给你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The world is in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.85,0:00:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,400)\pos(187.191,159.546)}{\fn黑体\fs28\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}六个月后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.36,0:00:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,数据我检查过了 我反复检查了好几遍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've checked the figures, I've checked them again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,结果都一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Always the same result.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:01:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这样设计隐患很大 可能害死数百万人的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The design is not safe. It could result in the death of millions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.09,0:01:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我求您了 趁一切为时未晚 停掉项目吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I beg of you, stop the project right now before it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.54,0:01:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,唉 真是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well... Goodness me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.10,0:01:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,克里夫先生 您果然是专家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Obviously, Mr Cleaver, you're the expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.40,0:01:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那您会停掉项目吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then you'll stop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,看来我别无选择了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It seems I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.23,0:01:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,原谅我失态了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh... Do excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.39,0:01:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,公职太忙 我饭都没吃好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Civic duties leave little time for a sandwich.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.02,0:01:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,您保证您会马上停掉项目吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you promise you'll stop it today?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.37,0:01:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么比人命更重要了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nothing is more important than human life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.38,0:01:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,您把我看成什么人了 疯子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do you take me for, some sort of maniac?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.54,0:01:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,您的计算结果 只有我一个人看到吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Am I right in thinking you've shown your results only to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就您一人 别人都不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just to you, no-one else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.85,0:01:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这就对了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wise move.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.66,0:01:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟您说 市长女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can tell you, Mrs. Mayor,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.55,0:01:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这事让我心里压力非常大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}this is such a weight off my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.43,0:01:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我几乎睡不着觉 我自己也不相信读数结果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've barely slept. I couldn't believe my own readings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.21,0:01:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,后果之严重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The scale of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.27,0:02:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,英伦三岛就从未见识过如此规模的破坏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Destruction like the British Isles has never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.58,0:02:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我不知情的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I didn't know better,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.44,0:02:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我简直要认为是有人有意让项目出问题了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd almost think that someone wanted this project to go wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像他们就是想抹掉整座城市似的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as though they intended this city should be wiped off the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地 我们有您的英明领导\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank goodness we've got you, our esteemed leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:03:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(600,0)\fn黑体\fs28\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\pos(189.538,171.6)}炸弹城
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn黑体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}卡迪夫中央火车站
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn黑体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}出站口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,什么我是谁啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do you mean, who the hell am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.73,0:03:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你又是谁啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克·哈克尼斯上校\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Jack Harkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你卖什么 我们不买\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Whatever you're selling, we are not buying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一边去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这应该就是米奇了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't tell me, this must be Mickey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,大麻烦来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Here comes trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,路上顺利吧 小里奇 -是米奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How are you doing, Ricky boy? - It's Mickey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,别理他 他逗你玩呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't listen to him, he's winding you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你真美\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You look fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:03:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,真甜蜜 瞧瞧这一对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aw, sweet! Look at these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么就没人抱我呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How come I never get any of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,先请我喝一杯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Buy me a drink first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你太难伺候 -但你绝不后悔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're such hard work. - But worth it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你找到了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you manage to find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.83,0:04:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,给你 -我现在哪都能去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There you go. - I can go anywhere now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.13,0:04:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过了 你用不着护照\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I told you, you don't need a passport.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,在审判星球和水晶金字塔上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's all very well going to Platform One
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,或一号平台也许用不着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in Justicia and the Glass Pyramid,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可万一要去巴西呢 我可能需要的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but what if we end up in Brazil? I might need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道 我什么都准备着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You see, I'm prepared for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,听这意思你要长住了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It sounds like you're staying, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在卡迪夫干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So what are you doing in Cardiff?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那边那位弹簧杰克男又是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And who the hell's Jumping Jack Flash?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我不介意你跟招风耳呆在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't mind you hanging out with Big Ears there. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.09,0:04:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说话呢 -自己照镜子去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oi! - Look in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但这家伙 我说不准 他有点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But this guy, I don't know, he's kinda. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,英俊吗 -倒不如说油头粉面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Handsome? - More like cheesy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,在21世纪俗语里油头粉面是好话还是坏话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Early 21st-century slang, is cheesy good or bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,坏的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.85,0:04:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但是坏意思是好的 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But bad means good, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说我就不英俊吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you saying I'm not handsome?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.21,0:04:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就是停一下补充燃料而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We just stopped off, we need to refuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,卡迪夫地下有一条裂谷横穿城市\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The thing is, Cardiff's got a rift through the middle of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然看不见 但就像地震裂缝一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's invisble, but it's like an earthquake fault
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这是不同维度之间的裂缝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}between different dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这裂缝1869年就闭合了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The rift was healed back in 1869.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.41,0:04:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢一个叫格温妮丝的女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thanks to a girl named Gwyneth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:04:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,因为有种叫做格尔斯的怪物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cause these creatures called the Gelth,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,试图从裂缝中穿越到这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they were using the rift as a gateway,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但她拯救了世界 关闭了裂缝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but she saved the world and closed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但尽管裂缝关闭了 一些小口子还是有的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But closing a rift leaves a scar,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这些口子会产生的能量对人类无害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and that scar generates energy, harmless to the human race...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但正是塔迪斯需要的 所以我们停几天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But perfect for the Tardis. So just park here for a coupl of days,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就停在这个裂口上 然后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}right on top of the scar. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,打开引擎 尽情吸收能量辐射\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Open up the engines, soak up the radiation. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就像给她加满油一样就能上路啦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like filling her up with petrol, and off we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.43,0:05:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,遨游时间 -和空间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Into time! - And space!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 瞧瞧你们个的样子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My God, have you seen yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你们觉得自己挺聪明 是不是 -是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You all think you're so clever, don't you? - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 -对头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah! - Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,还需再充24小时 所以我们有点空闲时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It should take another 24 hours, so we've got time to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那个老太太在盯着我们看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That old lady's staring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,可能在琢磨四个人挤在木头小警亭里做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Probably wondering what four people can do inside a small wooden box.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底是哪的上校 毒舌小队的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are you captain of - the Innuendo Squad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,慢着 不能丢下塔迪斯不管吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wait, the Tardis, can't just leave it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不会被发现吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}doesn't it get noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 这警亭外观是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, what's with the police box?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么是这个样子 -这是一种伪装设备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why does it look like that? - It's a cloaking device.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,名字是辟易线圈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's called a chameleon circuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,塔迪斯无论降落在哪里 都会作相应的伪装\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Tardis is meant to disguise itself wherever it lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,比如说如果降落在古罗马\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like if this was ancient Rome,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,她就会伪装成雕像基座之类的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it wiil be a statue on a plinth or somthing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但我降落在了1960年代 她伪装成警亭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I landed in the 1960s, it disguised itself as a police box,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,然后线圈就卡住了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and the circuit got stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她是参考已有的东西 真有这样的警亭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So it copied a real thing, there actually was police boxes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 就在街角\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, on street corners.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,在无线电和手机出现前 就用这个报警求助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Phone for help, Before they had radios and mobiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们逮捕了什么人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If they arrested somebody,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就可以把人塞进这里等待增援\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they could shove 'em inside till help came.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.65,0:06:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就跟小型监房似的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like a little prison cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那你为什么不修修线圈呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why don't you just fix the circuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢 你不喜欢吗 -我好喜欢啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I like it, don't you? - I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.61,0:06:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我说的就是这个意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But that's what I meant,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.86,0:06:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,现在没有警亭了 难道不会引起注意吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}there's no police boxes any more, so doesn't it get noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,里奇 我就跟你解释解释人类行为吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ricky, let me tell you something about human race,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你把一个神秘蓝箱子公然扔在闹市中心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you put a mysterious blue box slap bang in the middle of town,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,人们会怎么做 根本不管直接走开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}what do people do? Walk past it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.91,0:06:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,别说废话了 咱们去逛逛去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now stop your nagging, let's go and explore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么计划吗 -我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's the plan? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这是21世纪初的卡迪夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cardiff, early 21st century,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,而且今天刮的是 东风\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and the wind's coming from the... East.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我吧 这是全宇宙最安全的地方了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Trust me. The safest place in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这座位于卡迪夫市中心的核电站\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This nuclear power station right
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.61,0:06:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,将会为社会各阶层带来更多工作岗位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in the heart of Cardiff city will bring jobs for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如各位所见 身为市长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As you can see, as Lord Mayor,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我不得不批准一些激进的改建工程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've had to sanction some radical redevelopments.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不要拍照 我刚怎么说的来着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No photographs! What did I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.79,0:06:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,请您随意拍摄这项目 但不要拍我 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Take pictures of the project by all means, but not me, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,卡迪夫城堡将被拆除\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cardiff Castle will be demolished,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,为高大光荣的布莱德鲁格项目腾地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}allowing the Blaidd Drwg Project to rise up, tall and proud,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这将是威尔士工业的一座纪念碑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a monument to Welsh industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你们难免有人会对此心存质疑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And, yes, some of you might shiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.47,0:07:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"核电站"这个词\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The words "nuclear power station"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,和"人口中心"这个词\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and "major population centre"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,放到一起并不是那么和谐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}aren't exactly the happiest of bedfellows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但我以个人名誉保证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I give you my personal guarantee
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我活在这世上一天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that as long as I walk upon this Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就决不会有市民因此受伤害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}no harm will come to any of my citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,现在请举杯庆祝吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now drink up, a toast. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,敬未来 -敬未来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To the future! - The future!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And believe me. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这项目会璀璨夺目的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it will glow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了布莱恩女士 我是卡茜·索特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Excuse me, Mrs Blaine, my name's Cathy Salt,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我是《卡迪夫公报》记者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I represent the Cardiff Gazette.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉我不接受采访 我向来不自我宣传的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, I'm not doing interviews. I can't bear self-publicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但您听说过诅咒吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But are you aware of the curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思 卡茜是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Whatever do you mean? Cathy, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,卡茜·索特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cathy Salt,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,您的一些工程师是这么想的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that's what some of your engineers are saying
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱德鲁格项目被诅咒了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that the Blaidd Drwg Project is cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我听着挺傻的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sounds rather silly to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:07:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是这么想的 我只是报道些乡土新闻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's what I thought, I was just chasing a bit of local colour,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但有趣就有趣在你把这些事联系起来看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but the funny thing is when you start peacing it all together
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,确实会让人觉得有点怪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it does begin to look a bit odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说 -那些伤亡案件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In what way? - The deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那些与这个项目有关的死亡事件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The number of deaths associated with this project -
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.43,0:08:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,首先就是那整个欧洲安全观察团都死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}First of all, there was the entire team of European safety inspectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是法国人 这不能怪我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But they were French, it's not my fault,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,谁让他们只用威尔士语写"危险易爆"呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and, "Danger! Explosives!" was only written in Welsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就是卡迪夫文化遗产委员会的那起事故\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And the accident with the Cardiff Heritage Committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,经调查 那泳池触电事故完全是线路老化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The electrocution of that swimming pool was put down to natural wire entire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那还有建筑师呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And then the architect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,当时在下雨 能见度很低 我的车刹不住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was raining, visibility was low, my car simply couldn't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那最近的政府核能专家克里夫先生呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And then recently Mr Cleaver, the government's nuclear adviser.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,地面结冰滑倒了 -他脑袋都掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Slipped on an icy patch. - He was decapitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,冰面太滑摔得太惨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was a very icy patch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我看这些所谓故事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm afraid these stories are nothing more
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.29,0:08:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,无非就是坊间谣传罢了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}than typical small-town thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我实在没时间听这个 请您见谅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I really haven't got time. If you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不过在他死之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Except before he died,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,克里夫先生把他的发现发了一些在网上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr Cleaver posted some of his findings online.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.34,0:08:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.28,0:08:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,只要知道怎么找 他非常担心反应堆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you know where to look. He was concerned about the reactor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,又是那些技术上的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh! All that technical stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是抑压池的设计\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Specifically that the design of the suppression pool
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,会导致氢气复合器无法正常运行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}would cause the hydrogen recombiners to fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,从而引发安全壳隔离系统的急剧崩裂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}precipitating in the collapse of the containment isolation system,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,进而引发反应堆熔毁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and resulting meltdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你调查得还真是周详啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}who's been doing a homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我看 卡茜·索特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think. . .Cathy Salt. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.51,0:09:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我看你我应该私下里谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think you and I should have a word in private.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我的胃又不舒服了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, my little tummy's complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可能得去趟卫生间了 -我在这等着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We might have to make a detour to the ladies. - I'll wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不像话 咱们女生一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, come on! All girls together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才你的那些古怪理论说到哪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So you were saying? These outlandish theories of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,看来我们来得真及时啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It sounds like we got here just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,请继续 -核物理我了解的不多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Continue. - Well, I don't know much about nuclear physics,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但根据我的理解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but from what I could make out,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,克里夫认为整个建筑都会炸上天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cleaver was saying the whole project could go up,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,比切尔诺贝利还要惨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}worse than Chernobyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,里面的灯坏了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is there something wrong with the lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这破灯总是一闪一闪的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, they're always on the blink.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道发了多少文件要求修一修了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't tell you how many memos I've sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:09:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,接着说 切尔诺贝利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So...Chernobyl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:10:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅如此 而且要糟上一千倍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Apparently, but a thousand times worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道听起来有点假\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean it sounds absurd,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定会有安全措施的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}there must be so many safety regulations,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但是听克里夫的意思 这会是核爆浩劫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but Cleaver seemed to be talking about a nuclear holocaust.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他说简直就像有人故意似的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He almost made it sound deliberate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是《星期日泰晤士报》那种大报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean we're hardly The Sunday Times,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是《卡迪夫公报》\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we're only the Cardiff Gazette,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.23,0:10:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们还是有义务揭露真相的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but we do have a duty to report the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那你打算刊发这个消息吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you're going to print this information?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗 你听起来… -嗓子疼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you all right? You sound a bit... - Sore throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有点喉咙痒而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just a little tickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不过请告诉我 你是不是打算\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But tell me, do you intend
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.05,0:10:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,将这个消息公之于众 -我不得不如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to make this information public? - I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不过告诉你 我男朋友觉得我疯了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mind you, my boyfriend thinks I'm mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们下个月就要结婚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're getting married next month
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他说如果我闹出了大事 我会丢了饭碗的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and he says if I cause a fuss I could lose my job,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,而我们手头正紧呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}just when we need the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,男朋友 -杰弗里 公务员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Boyfriend? - Jeffrey, civil servant...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就是个普通人 但也是我的心上人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's nothing exciting, but he's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,婚礼是什么时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When's the wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,19号 其实就是为了堵我妈的嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The 19th. It's really just to stop my mother from nagging,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.85,0:11:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我看怀了孕 不结也不行了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but the baby sort of clinched it I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你怀孕了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're with child?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,三个月了 外形上还看不出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Three months. It's not showing yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怀上孩子也是个意外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It wasn't planned, it was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不过是个甜蜜的意外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nice accident, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.31,0:11:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜你 -谢谢您\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Congratulations. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢 你有孩子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How about you? You got any kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你结婚了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is there a Mr Blaine?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,离了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我自力更生了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm all on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我曾有一个大家庭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I had quite a sizeable family once upon a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟们可爱极了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wonderful brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,个个胆子都大得很\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, they were bold!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们都不在了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But all of them gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你说得对 也许我是遭了诅咒了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe you're right. Maybe I'm cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不这么想 怎么会呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, no, I don't think so, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're very kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.01,0:11:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我还得再待一会儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you don't mind, I might be a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你先走吧 也许改天我们接着谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You run along. Perhaps we could do this another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.87,0:12:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,您还好吗 -好得很\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you all right? - Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不如这样吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}OK, I tell you what,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我把详细资料放在您办公室里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll leave my details with your office.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.29,0:12:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢您和我说话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thanks for talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,也谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你就满嘴扯谎吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're lying through your teeth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,原来那白色的东西是大尖牙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean, it turns out the white things are tusks,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,大尖牙啊 它醒过来 非常不高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I mean, tusks! And it's woken and it's not happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么就没发现它在那 -我们15个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How could you not know it was there? - 15 of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,一丝不挂 然后我就说 "不是我干的"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}naked, and I'm going like, "Nothing to do with me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,然后它吼叫起来 我们就赶紧跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then it roars, and we are running!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,死了命地跑啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh my God, we are running!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,布拉科维奇摔倒了 然后我转身对他说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Brakovitch falls, so I turn to him, and I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我就说我们该左拐吧 -我就是这么说的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I knew we should've turned left! - That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的话我一个字都不信 太扯了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't believe a word you say! That is so brilliant!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.45,0:12:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的衣服拿回来了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you ever get your clothes back?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 我一把他扶起来就往船上跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I just picked him up and went right for the ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,全速疯跑 一直开着船冲进了太空\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}full throttle. Didn't stop while I hit the space.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我全身那个抖啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean I was shaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,太不可思议了 我吓死了都\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was unbelievable! It freaked me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,等我停下飞船 已经到了15光年开外了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now and by the time I got there I was fifteen lightyears away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.19,0:13:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我就想 当初为什么要来呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then I realized, why this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我就没一天安宁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I was having such a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn黑体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}《西部邮报》\N新市长 新卡迪夫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,据情报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}According to intelligence,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,目标是斯利辛家族最后一个幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the target is the last surviving member of the Slitheen family,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,来自拉克西科里科弗拉帕多里斯星的犯罪家族\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a criminal sect from the planet Raxacoricofallapatorious,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,假扮成人类\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}masquerading as a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,披着一张人皮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Zipped inside a skin suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,进攻计划 我们执行57-56号基础战略\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}OK! Plan of attack, we assume a basic 57-56 strategy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,封锁一楼所有进出口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}covering all available exits on the ground floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,博士 你和她正面对抗 守住1号门\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doctor, you go face to face, that'll designate exit 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我守2号门 洛斯3号 米奇4号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll cover exit 2. Rose, exit 3. Mickey Smith, exit 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.82,0:13:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,听明白了没\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have you got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 该谁发号施令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Excuse me. Who's in charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 等候指示 长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sorry. Awaiting orders, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:13:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好 计划如下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Right, here's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.37,0:14:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就听他的 好计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like he said. Nice plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,还有补充吗 -举枪致敬吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Anything else? - Present arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了 -准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ready. - Ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了 -准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ready. - Ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,设置快速拨号 -好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Speed dial? - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,完成 -就绪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ready. - Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.55,0:14:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,地狱见吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}See you in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 我来见市长大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hello, I've come to see the Lord Mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,您有预约吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have you got an appointment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不 就是个老朋友顺道看看 给她个惊喜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, just an old friend, passing by, bit of a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真想看看她什么表情 -她正在用茶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't wait to see her face. - She's just having a cup of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你只管进去告诉她 博士来看她了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just go in there and tell her the Doctor would like to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,哪位博士 -就是博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doctor who? - Just the Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,原话告诉她 博士来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell her exactly that, the Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,请您稍等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hang on a tick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,市长说她很感谢您突然来访\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Lord Mayor says thank you for popping by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,她也很想和您叙叙旧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She'd love to have a chat but,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.11,0:15:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 她实在是忙不过来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}em... She's up to her eyes in paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,您可以预约下周再来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Perhaps if you could make an appointment for next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,她正在爬窗逃走 是不是 -没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She's climbing out of the window, isn't she? - Yes, she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,斯利辛朝北逃窜了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Slitheen heading north!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这就去 -收到 完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On my way. - Over and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,别伤害市长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Leave the Mayor alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,玛格丽特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Margaret!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,4号出口是谁把守\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who's on exit 4?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是米奇 -我来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That was Mickey! - Here I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,大傻子米奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mickey the idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,别怪他 她总不能跑得比我们快吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, be fair, she's not exactly gonna outrun us, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,她有传送器 这是作弊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She's got a teleport, that's cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这下我们别想抓她了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now we're never gonna get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,博士玩传送器玩得可溜了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, the Doctor's very good at teleports.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以陪你玩一整天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I could do this all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这是公然迫害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is persecution!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛总追着我不放 我怎么惹着你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why can't you leave me alone? What did I ever do to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你想杀我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You tried to kill me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,还打算毁掉整个地球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and destroy this entire planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.79,0:16:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那些先不算\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Apart from that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个斯利辛 被困在地球上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So you're a Slitheen, you're on Earth, you're trapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:17:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你家人全死了 但你传送走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your family get killed, but you teleport out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.09,0:17:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一刻逃了出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just in the neck of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你却不想逃走 那你打算做什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have no means of escape, what do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你建了一座核电站 但是目的是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You build a nuclear power station, but what for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我这是做慈善 我已经意识到错了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A philanthropic gesture. I've learnt the error of my ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你偏偏盖在裂缝上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And it just so happens to be on top of the rift.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,什么裂缝 -时空裂缝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What rift would that be? - A rift in space and time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这个核电站熔毁 整个地球都会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If this went into meltdown, the entire planet would...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这个核电站就是设计成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This station is designed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦启用立即爆炸的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to explode the minute it reaches capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就没人发现吗 伦敦那边就没人核查这个吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Didn't anyone notice? Doesn't anyone in London check this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.18,0:17:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是卡迪夫 伦敦才没人理我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're in Cardiff, London doesn't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.14,0:17:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就算整个南威尔士沉进海里他们也不会注意到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}South Wales could fall into the sea and they wouldn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么一股威尔士人腔调\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh. I sound like a Welshman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,老天 我入乡随俗了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}God help me, I've gone native.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,她建这个做什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But why would she do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那么大的爆炸她自己也活不成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A great big explosion should only end up killing herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,她有名字 -她都不是个人 是个怪物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She's got a name. - She's not even a she, she's a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但她很聪明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, but she's clever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.56,0:17:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,妙极了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:18:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这是巨型三相波动力学推进器吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that a tribophysical waveform macro-kinetic extrapolator?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,说得非常正确\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Couldn't have put it better myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,天才 这不是你造的吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ooh, genius! You didn't build this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,一点小爱好罢了 造些小东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have my hobbies. Little tinckering.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 我是说这不可能是你造的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, you really didn't build this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你的水平还不够 -我猜是她偷来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Way beyond you. - I bet she stole it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是我偶然得来的 -这是武器吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It fell into my hands. - Is it a weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是传送器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's transport.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,如果反应堆爆炸了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You see, if the reactor blows,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,裂缝开启 引发了大规模灾难\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the rift opens, phenomenal cosmic disaster
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但这个东西能把你罩在力场里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but this thing shrouds you in a force field,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就像一个能量防护罩 保你安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you have this energy bubble, so you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你输入坐标 站在上面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then you feed it coordinates, stand on top,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,乘着冲击波一路飞出太阳系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and ride the concussion all the way out of the solar system.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是个冲浪板 -是全维度冲浪板\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a surfboard. - A pan-dimensional surfboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,本来可以成功的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And it would have worked,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我本可以一路飞出这个垃圾星球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd have surfed away from this dead-end dump,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,回到我的家园\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}back to civilisation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你炸掉整个星球就为了搭个车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'd blow up a planet to get a lift?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.71,0:18:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就像踩在蚂蚁窝上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like stepping on an anthill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这个名字你怎么看 -什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How did you think of the name? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱德鲁格 是威尔士语\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Blaidd Drwg? It's Welsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.43,0:18:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 但是你怎么想到的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know, but how did you think of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.60,0:18:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,随手挑的 没什么特别\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I chose it at random, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.07,0:18:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道 听着顺耳 有什么关系吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I dunno, it just sounded good. Does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱德鲁格\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Blaidd Drwg.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思 -恶狼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's it mean? - Bad Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我听过这个词 恶狼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've heard that before, "Bad Wolf."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我听见过好几次了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've heard that lots of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去哪里 这个词就跟到哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everywhere we go, two words following us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,恶狼 -怎么可能跟着我们呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bad Wolf. - How can they be following us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.48,0:19:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么 巧合而已嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nah, just a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像听见广播里的一个词\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like hearing a word on the radio,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉整天听似的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}then hearing it all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么大不了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,还有正事要做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,玛格丽特 我们要送你回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Margaret, we're gonna take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,慢着 这不就等于轻易放她走了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hold on, isn't that the easier option like letting her go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.51,0:19:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,真是难以置信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't believe it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们真要去拉克西…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we actually get to go to Raxa. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 是拉克西科里…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wait a minute! Raxacori...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,拉克西科里科弗拉帕多里斯星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Raxacoricofallapatorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,拉克西科里科 -弗拉帕多里斯星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Raxacorico... - Fallapatorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,拉克西科里科弗拉帕多里斯星 -对了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Raxacoricofallapatorious! - That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.61,0:19:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我说对了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.53,0:19:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那里是有死刑的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They have the death penalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,多年以前斯利辛家族\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The family Slitheen was trialed
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:20:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,在缺席情况下被审判有罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in its absence many years ago and found guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不允许上诉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}With no chance of appeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,根据政府法令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}According to the statutes of government,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我一回去就要被处决\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the moment I return I am to be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么看 博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do you make of that, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,带我回家 你就带我走向死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Take me home, and you take me to my death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.47,0:20:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是我的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这飞船简直不可思议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This ship is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,非常卓越 你怎么能让它里外差距这么大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's superb! How do you get the outside around the inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我会告诉你其中奥秘吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like I'd give you the secret, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这下被你打败我心里也平衡多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I almost feel better about being defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们之前毫无胜算 这可是神之科技\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We never stood a chance, this is the technology of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,别膜拜我 我会是个坏神的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't worship me. I'd make a very bad god.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是神就不会让你消停的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You wouldn't get a day off for starters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克 大家伙怎么样了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jack, how are we doing, big fella?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.71,0:20:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这个外推器是顶级的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This extrapolator's top of the range.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你从哪儿弄到它的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 哪个气闸甩卖上吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know. Some airlock sale?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:20:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是大抢了一场吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It must have been a great big heist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,它充满能量 -我们能用它补充燃料吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's stacked with power. - But we can use it for fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,和这船不兼容 但能缩短12小时充能时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not compatible, but it should knock off about 12 hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.65,0:21:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们早上就能出发了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we'll be ready to go by morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们晚上就困在这儿了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then we're stuck here overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.07,0:21:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我不急\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm in no hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有个囚犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've got a prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这个警察电话亭真成了警察电话亭了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The police box is really a police box.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.06,0:21:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但你们不仅是警察\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're not just police, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你们要带我去刑场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Since you're taking me to my death,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这让你们变成了我的行刑人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that makes you my executioners.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你们每个人都是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Each and every one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.29,0:21:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但你罪有应得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, you deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.01,0:21:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你话说得轻巧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're very quick to say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你的双手很快就会浸满我的鲜血\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're very quick to soak your hands in my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来 你的罪又能比我轻多少呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Which makes you better than me how, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,长夜漫漫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Long night ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,看看谁能直视我的双眼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's see who can look me in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这外面好冷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's freezing out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.94,0:22:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,也比那里好点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Better than in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.66,0:22:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她罪有应得 她是个斯利辛 我不在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She does deserve it, she's a Slitheen, I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.99,0:22:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,只是在那盒子里感觉怪怪的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's just...weird in that box.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.98,0:22:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我其实不需要我的护照\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't really need my passport.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想 我们可以去喝一杯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've been thinking, you know, we could...go have a drink,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.66,0:23:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,吃点披萨什么的 就我们俩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}have a pizza or something, just you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.99,0:23:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好主意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That'd be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,如果塔迪斯直到早上都走不了 我们可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I mean, if the Tardis can't leave until morning we could...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.58,0:23:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,去酒店 共度良宵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go to a hotel, spend the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.01,0:23:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想 我带了钱 -行啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean if you want to, I've got some money. - OK. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.14,0:23:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真没关系吗 -没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that all right? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好 这附近有几家酒吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cool...there's a couple of bars round here,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.84,0:23:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以去逛逛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we should give 'em a go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要去告诉他一声吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you have to go and tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.49,0:23:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这和他无关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's none of his business.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.06,0:23:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So what's on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.24,0:23:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么 只是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nothing, just...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.50,0:23:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜你平时不是这样的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I gather it's not always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.47,0:23:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不得不等待\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Having to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.26,0:24:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜你总是最先离开的那个 博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I bet you're always the first to leave, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.24,0:24:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,从不多想后果 只管甩手走人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Never mind the consequences, off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.26,0:24:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你屠杀我的家人后就跑向宇宙了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You butchered my family and then ran for the stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.17,0:24:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我说的对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.96,0:24:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但这次不会了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But not this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.40,0:24:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你终于自食其果了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At last you have consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.32,0:24:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉如何 -我没有屠杀它们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How does it feel? - I didn't butcher them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.63,0:24:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,别回答 这就是她想要的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't answer back, that's what she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.48,0:24:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.41,0:24:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那你呢 你进行了紧急瞬移\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What about you? You had an emergency teleport.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.10,0:24:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你没把它们一起带到安全之处 对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You didn't zap them to safety, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.43,0:24:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,它只能带一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It only carries one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.09,0:24:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我得在无坐标情况下飞行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I had to fly without co-ordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.15,0:24:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我最后降落在犬岛的一个垃圾桶里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I ended up in a skip on the Isle of Dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.02,0:24:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这一点也不有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It wasn't funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.69,0:24:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.32,0:24:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,其实挺搞笑的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is a bit funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.95,0:24:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以提最后一个要求吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do I get a last request?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.86,0:25:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,要看是什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Depends what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.26,0:25:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我开始有点喜欢人类生活了 这些仪式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I grew quite fond of my little human life, all those rituals.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.01,0:25:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,刷牙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The brushing of the teeth
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.31,0:25:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,还有他们烹饪东西的复杂方式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and the complicated way they cook things.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.21,0:25:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,在海湾边有个小餐馆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's a little restaurant, just round the bay,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.36,0:25:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是我挺喜欢的一个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it became quite a favourite of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.14,0:25:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你想要的 最后一餐吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that what you want, a last meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.65,0:25:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我难道没有这权利吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't I have rights?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.23,0:25:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她不会试图逃跑才怪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, like she's not gonna try to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.81,0:25:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我永远无法从博士手上逃跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Except I can never escape the Doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.73,0:25:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么危险的呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so where's the danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.01,0:25:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想你能不能做到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wonder if you could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.16,0:25:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,和一个你要杀掉的生物共进晚餐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To sit with a creature you're about to kill and take supper.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.07,0:25:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,看你吃不吃得下饭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How strong is your stomach?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.60,0:25:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,能做到 -真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Strong enough. - I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.45,0:25:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我看过你与敌人战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've seen you fight your enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.37,0:25:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,现在与它们共进晚餐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now dine with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.70,0:26:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会让我改主意的 -证明给我看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You won't change my mind. - Prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.13,0:26:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,外面有人类\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are people out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.65,0:26:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你哪怕溜出去一秒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you slip away just for one second,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.40,0:26:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就会身处险境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they'll be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.48,0:26:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 我有这东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Except... I've got these.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.23,0:26:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩各带一个 如果她离你超过三米\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You both wear one. If she moves more than ten feet away, zzzt!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.66,0:26:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,她就会受到一万伏特电击\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She gets zapped by 10, 000 volts.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.65,0:26:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,玛格丽特 你想出去吃晚餐吗 我请客\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Margaret, would you like to come out to dinner? My treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.86,0:26:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,铐在一起吃晚餐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dinner in bondage.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.94,0:26:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It works for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.78,0:27:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们出来约会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Here we are out on a date,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.49,0:27:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,而你却连我的真名都没问过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and you haven't even asked my proper name.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.45,0:27:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是约会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.24,0:27:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字 -布隆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's your name? - Blon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.43,0:27:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫布隆·菲富奇·帕萨梅戴·斯利辛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm Blon Fel Fotch Passameer-Day Slitheen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.25,0:27:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这将是我死亡证明上的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's what it'll say on my death certificate.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.96,0:27:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你 布隆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nice to meet you, Blon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.71,0:27:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我确信这点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.56,0:27:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,看 那就是我在当玛格丽特时住的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, that's where I was living as Margaret,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.49,0:27:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,一个很好的小公寓 那里 在顶上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a nice little flat, over there. On the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.24,0:27:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,就在亮灯的那一间旁边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Next to the one with the light on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.15,0:27:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,两间卧室 海景房 我当时很高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Two bedrooms, bay-side view, I was rather content.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.85,0:27:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜我再也见不到它了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't suppose I'll see it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.55,0:27:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Suppose not.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.46,0:28:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.75,0:28:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不客气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.05,0:28:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我 博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell me then, Doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.51,0:28:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你对我们这个物种了解多少\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}what do you know of our species?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.96,0:28:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我看到的那些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Only what I've seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.85,0:28:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 举例来说 在极端情况下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you know, for example, in extreme cases,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.26,0:28:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,当她的生命受到威胁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when her life is in danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.19,0:28:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,一个雌性拉克西科里科弗拉帕多里斯星人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a female Raxacoricofallapatorian
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.23,0:28:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可以在她手指内生成一个毒镖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}can manufacture a poison dart within her own finger?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.60,0:28:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 -只是测试一下嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, I did. - Just checking.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.60,0:28:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And one more thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.74,0:28:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是你我之间的小秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}between you and me...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.48,0:28:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,作为自救的最终手段\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As a final resort,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.43,0:28:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,其余的毒素可以从肺部呼出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the excess poison can be exhaled through the lungs.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.39,0:28:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这样好闻多了 现在点菜吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's better. Now then, what d'you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.50,0:28:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,牛排看起来不错 牛排薯条\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mmm, steak looks nice. Steak and chips!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.91,0:29:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,前阵子博士带我去了一个星球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Doctor took me to this planet a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.41,0:29:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,比地球冷多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was much colder than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.42,0:29:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把这里叫做哭泣的女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They called it Women Wept.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.83,0:29:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这个星球被叫做哭泣的女人是因为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The planet was actually called Women Wept coz
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.84,0:29:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你俯瞰它 有一片巨大的大陆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if you looked at it from above, there's this huge continent,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.47,0:29:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好像没什么棱角\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}like all curved round.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.32,0:29:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,看上去就像个女人 在悲泣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It sort of looked like a woman, lamenting.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.79,0:29:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 我们去过这么一片海滩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, my God, and we went to this beach, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.02,0:29:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人 没有建筑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No people, no buildings,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.53,0:29:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,只有这片绵延千里的海滩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}just this beach like a thousand miles across.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.96,0:29:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么事发生了 与太阳有关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Something had happened, something to do with the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.12,0:29:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 但是大海一下子就冻上了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know, but the sea had just frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.31,0:29:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,像是在刹那间 在风暴中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like in a split second, in the middle of a storm, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.59,0:29:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,海浪与浮沫都冻了起来 直到海平线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Waves and foam, just frozen, all the way out to the horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.89,0:29:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在午夜 我们在这些海浪下漫步\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Midnight, we walk underneath these waves,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.54,0:29:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,有百尺高 都是冰做的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a hundred feet tall and made of ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.57,0:29:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我在和特丽莎·德莱尼约会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm going out with Trisha Delaney.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.12,0:29:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.77,0:29:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.30,0:29:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,店里的那个特丽莎吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Trisha from the shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.87,0:29:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,对 罗伯·德莱尼的妹妹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, Rob Delaney's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.40,0:30:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,她人很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, she's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.71,0:30:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,她有点胖 -她减肥了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She's a bit big. - She lost weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.55,0:30:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直不在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've been away.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.49,0:30:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真为你高兴 她很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, good for you, she's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.68,0:30:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,再和我多说说这星球 -就这么多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So tell us more about this planet, then. - That was it, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.14,0:30:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,公开处刑会采用缓慢的处决方法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Public execution's a slow death.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.35,0:30:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,它们会准备醋酸稀溶液\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They prepare a thin acetic acid,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.77,0:30:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,把我放进一个大锅里煮熟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}lower me into the cauldron...and boil me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.52,0:30:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,酸度正好能让皮肤剥离\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The acidity is perfectly gauged to strip away the skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.68,0:30:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,而内脏则掉入溶液里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Internal organs fall out into the liquid
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.80,0:30:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我就变成汤了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I become soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.00,0:30:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但依然活着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.11,0:30:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,依然在惨叫 -我不是制定法律的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Still screaming. - I don't make the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.11,0:30:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但你是执行者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you deliver it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.86,0:30:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你会留下来观刑吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Will you stay to watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.87,0:30:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我还能做什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What else can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.47,0:31:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,斯利辛是个大家族 我们还有很多族人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Slitheen family's huge, there's a lot more of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.16,0:31:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,遍布宇宙各地 带我去找他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}all scattered off-world. Take me to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.59,0:31:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,带我去安全的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Take me somewhere safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.51,0:31:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但你就会死灰复燃 -我保证不会的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But then you'll just start again. - I promise I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.59,0:31:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你在那副人皮里呆太久了 已经忘记了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've been in that skin-suit too long, you've forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.72,0:31:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,曾经有个真正的玛格丽特·布莱恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There used to be a real Margaret Blaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.06,0:31:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你杀了她 剥了她的皮用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You killed her and stripped her and used the skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.97,0:31:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你在用一个死去女人的嘴请求宽恕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're pleading for mercy out of a dead woman's lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.96,0:31:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我已经习惯了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Perhaps I have got used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.29,0:31:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,作为人类生活 普通生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A human life, an ordinary life.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.37,0:31:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这就想要这么多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's all I'm asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.37,0:31:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,给我个机会 博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Give me a chance, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.07,0:31:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以改 -我不相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can change. - I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.42,0:31:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在想做什么 -不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So what do you want to do now? - Don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.75,0:31:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以去酒店看看还有没有房间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We could ask about hotels.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.48,0:31:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那特丽莎·德莱尼怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What would Trisha Delaney say?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.63,0:31:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,说的也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.49,0:31:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那边有个酒吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's a bar down there
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.19,0:31:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,名字好像是西班牙语什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with a Spanish name or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.24,0:31:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本不喜欢特丽莎·德莱尼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't even like Trisha Delaney!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.07,0:31:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 你知道个屁啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh is that right? What the hell do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.27,0:32:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,可我了解你 我也知道她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know you! And I know her,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.61,0:32:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这永远不会发生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I know that's never gonna happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.68,0:32:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你觉得你在骗谁呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so who do you think you're kidding? !
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.85,0:32:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,至少我知道她在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At least I know where she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.86,0:32:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There we are, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.03,0:32:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这和特丽莎无关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's got nothing to do with Trisha,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.76,0:32:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,都是因为我 -你离开了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}this is all about me! - You left me!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.03,0:32:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们当时处的很好 很快乐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We were nice, we were happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.46,0:32:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你给我一个吻和他跑了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}then you give me a kiss and run off with him
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.28,0:32:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我觉得自己一文不值\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and you make me feel like nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.87,0:32:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,洛斯 我一文不值\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Rose! I was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.99,0:32:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我不被允许和一个店里的蠢女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't even go out with a stupid girl
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.66,0:32:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,一起约会 因为你一通电话我就得跑过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}from a shop because you pick up the phone and I comes running.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.01,0:32:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我的用处吗 洛斯 备胎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean, is that what I am, Rose - standby?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.30,0:32:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不是该坐在这里等你一辈子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Am I just supposed to sit here for the rest of my life waiting for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.63,0:32:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我真的会的 -对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because I will! - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.82,0:32:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你保证上次见面后我就变了 博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I promise you I've changed since we last met, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.04,0:32:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就在今天 有个女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There was this girl, just today,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.32,0:32:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一个年轻女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a young thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.03,0:33:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,危险的是 她快要查出真相了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And something of a danger, she was getting too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.94,0:33:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉嗜血的欲望升腾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I felt the blood lust rising,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.43,0:33:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就像家族教给我那样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}just as the family taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.55,0:33:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我几乎不假思索就要杀了她 然后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was going to kill her without a thought. Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.98,0:33:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我停手了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.16,0:33:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,她就活在某个地方 现在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She's alive somewhere, right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.42,0:33:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,她在这城市中奔走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}she's walking round this city,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.74,0:33:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我可以改变 也改变了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because I can change, I did change.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.69,0:33:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我无法证明 -我相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know I can't prove it. - I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.84,0:33:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就知道我可以变得更好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then you know I'm capable of better.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.54,0:33:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这不能说明什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It doesn't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.36,0:33:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是留了她一命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I spared her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.60,0:33:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你放一个人走了 但这不是什么新鲜事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You let one of them go, but that's nothing new.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.70,0:33:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你时不时地放走一个 要么是因为她笑了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Every now and then, a little victim's spared because she smiled,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.97,0:33:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,或是因为他有雀斑 亦或是他们求饶了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}cos he's got freckles, cos they begged.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.53,0:33:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是这样让自己心安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And that's how you live with yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.82,0:33:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样心安理得继续大肆屠杀的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that's how you slaughter millions,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.87,0:33:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,因为有时候 一时兴起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because once in a while, on a whim,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.83,0:33:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,如果哪天心情好 你才会放人一马\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if the wind's in the right direction, you happen to be kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.12,0:34:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一个杀人犯才知道这点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Only a killer would know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.85,0:34:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.58,0:34:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,以我看来 你那有趣而无忧无虑的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}From what I've seen, your funny little,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.46,0:34:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,人生的尾迹里留下的只有毁灭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}happy-go-lucky life leaves devastation in its wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.79,0:34:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,总是前进是因为你不敢回头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Always moving on, cos you dare not go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.16,0:34:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,玩弄无数人的性命 你可能真像上帝一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Playing with so many people's lives, you might as well be a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.34,0:34:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你是对的 博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you're right, Doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.99,0:34:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你一点都没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.60,0:34:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有时 你会放过一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sometimes...you let one go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.30,0:34:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,放过我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.90,0:34:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是让你离开他 因为我知道这不公平\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not asking you to leave him, cos I know that's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.00,0:34:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但我只是需要点什么 一点保证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I just need something, some sort of promise,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.45,0:34:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,保证就算你回来也是为了我回来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that when you do come back, you're coming back for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.51,0:34:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那是打雷吗 -有什么关系呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that thunder? - Does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.52,0:34:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是打雷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's not thunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.25,0:34:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在斯利辛家族 我们别无选择\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In the family Slitheen, we had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.84,0:34:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我在十三岁时被迫第一次杀人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was made to carry out my first kill at 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.58,0:34:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我当时拒绝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I'd refused,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.62,0:35:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲就会把我喂给剧毒蛆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}my father would have fed me to the venom grubs!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.94,0:35:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我是个杀手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I'm a killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.08,0:35:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那也是因为我生来就为了杀戮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it's because I was born to kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.68,0:35:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我只知道杀戮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it's all I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.85,0:35:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,博士 你到底有没有在听我说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doctor? Are you even listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.61,0:35:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你能听到吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.87,0:35:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在请求宽恕 -听\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm begging for my life! - Listen, shush.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.09,0:35:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 你就只管走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ah, go on then, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.01,0:35:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是又是他啊 是博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's him again, isn't it? ! It's the Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.54,0:35:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,总是博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's always the Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.60,0:35:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,从来都是博士 而不是我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's always gonna be the Doctor, it's never me!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.94,0:35:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我的手铐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My handcuffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.10,0:35:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你不会想逃跑了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't think you're running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.96,0:35:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟定你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, I'm sticking with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.86,0:35:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,约个会结果约成了这个样子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Some date this turned out to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.25,0:36:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是裂缝 裂缝正在开启\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's the rift. The rift's opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.42,0:36:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底在干嘛 -它失控了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What the hell are you doing? - It just went crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.79,0:36:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是裂缝 时间空间都在断裂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's the rift! Time and space are ripping apart,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.71,0:36:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,整个城市都会消失\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the whole city's gonna disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.48,0:37:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是那个推进器 我已经断开连接了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's the extrapolator! I've disconnected it,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.04,0:37:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但它依然在给引擎供能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but it's still feeding off the engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.53,0:37:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,它在利用塔迪斯 我无法阻止它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's using the Tardis! I can't stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.74,0:37:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,别想卡迪夫了 它会把整个星球割裂的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Never mind Cardiff, it's gonna rip open the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.35,0:37:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 发生什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What is it? ! What's happening? !
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.36,0:37:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我的妙计生效了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, just little me!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.47,0:37:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,敢轻举妄动的话我就把她撕成碎片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One wrong move and she snaps like a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.94,0:37:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我早该猜到的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I might have known.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.15,0:37:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我整晚都在听你胡扯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've had you bleating all night,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.86,0:37:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,可怜虫 现在闭嘴吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}poor baby, now shut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.83,0:37:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你 小飞人 把外推器放到我脚边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You! Fly boy! Put the extrapolator at my feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.56,0:37:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.49,0:37:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我计划的一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just as I planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.54,0:38:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你得炸掉核电站才行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought you needed to blow up the nuclear power station.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.46,0:38:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,如果失败 要是有人来抓我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Failing that, if I were to be...arrested,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.99,0:38:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那么任何有能力追踪我的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}then anyone capable of tracking me down
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.59,0:38:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,自己就拥有相当先进的科技\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}would have considerable technology of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.95,0:38:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 他们就会被推进器吸引过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Therefore...they would be captivated by the extrapolator.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.96,0:38:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是像你这样爱四处收集的人 博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Especially a magpie mind like yours, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.74,0:38:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,所以外推器被设定成执行B计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So the extrapolator was programmed to go to Plan B -
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.48,0:38:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,锁定最近的异星能量源开启裂缝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to lock on to the nearest alien power source and open the rift.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.60,0:38:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,而它找到了如此巨大的能量源\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And what a power source it found...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.08,0:38:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我的计划又可以启动了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm back on schedule...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.93,0:38:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.20,0:38:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,裂缝将会震荡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The rift's gonna convulse,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.23,0:38:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你会毁了这星球 -而你们会为它陪葬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you'll destroy the planet. - And you with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.88,0:38:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,而我将乘着这块飞板\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}While I ride this board
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.54,0:38:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,越过炼狱之顶飞向自由\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}over the crest of the inferno all the way to freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.83,0:38:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,退后 小子们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stand back, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.02,0:39:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我要走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Surf's up!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.08,0:39:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,开启裂缝意味着你会把这飞船扯成两半\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course, opening the rift means you'll pull this ship apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.30,0:39:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So sue me!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.38,0:39:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这不像是老式的能量源\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not just any old power source.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.37,0:39:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这是塔迪斯 我的塔迪斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's the Tardis, my Tardis.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.59,0:39:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,全宇宙最好的飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The best ship in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.42,0:39:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,它会碎成美丽的碎片的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It'll make wonderful scrap.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.98,0:39:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那道光是什么 -是塔迪斯之心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's that light? ! - The heart of the Tardis.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.54,0:39:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这飞船是有生命的 你打开了它的灵魂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This ship's alive. You've opened its soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.58,0:39:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.28,0:39:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如此明亮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.00,0:39:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,看着它 玛格丽特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look at it, Margaret.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.80,0:39:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真美\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.51,0:39:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,看看里面 布隆·菲富奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look inside, Blon Fel Fotch.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.16,0:39:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,看着这光\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look at the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.29,0:40:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.21,0:40:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,别看 站着别动 闭上眼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't look! Stay there, close your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.89,0:40:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克 快来把它关上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jack, come on, shut it, shut it all down!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.37,0:40:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,洛斯 去那边的控制板\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Rose, that panel over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.56,0:40:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,把所有开关扳到右侧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}turn all the switches to the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.09,0:41:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮 谢谢你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nicely done. Thank you, all.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.12,0:41:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,玛格丽特怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What happened to Margaret?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.05,0:41:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是被烧光了 自我执行了死刑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Must've got burnt up, carried out her own death sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.41,0:41:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我觉得她没死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I don't think she's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.83,0:41:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那她会去哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then where'd she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.47,0:41:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她看到了塔迪斯之心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She looked into the heart of the Tardis.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.07,0:41:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,即便是我也不知道效力有多强\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Even I don't know how strong that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.10,0:41:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,而飞船会心灵感应\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And the ship's telepathic,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.03,0:41:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,像我告诉你的那样 洛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}like I told you, Rose,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.33,0:41:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,它会进入你的脑海 翻译异星语言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it gets inside your head, translates alien languages.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.73,0:41:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,也许纯能量可以翻译所有的思想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe the raw energy can translate all sorts of thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.17,0:41:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,她在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Here she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.84,0:41:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,她变成一只蛋了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She's an egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.92,0:41:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,退化到童年时代了 -她成了一只蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Regressed to her childhood. - She's an egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.79,0:41:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,她可以重新开始新生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She can start again. Live a life from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.48,0:41:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们带她回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If we take her home,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.70,0:41:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,把她交给一个能好好抚养她的家庭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}give her to a different family who bring her up properly,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.22,0:41:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她可能可以正常成长 -也可能更坏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}she might be all right. - Or she might be worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.39,0:41:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这是她的选择\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's her choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.44,0:41:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,她变成了一只蛋 -一只蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She's an egg. - She's an egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.28,0:41:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 米奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, my God, Mickey!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.95,0:42:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们充能完毕 可以离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We are all powered up. We can leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.67,0:42:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,裂缝的开启让飞船充满了能量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Opening the rift filled us up with energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.31,0:42:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以出发了 如果没问题的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we can go. If that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.09,0:42:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.76,0:43:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,米奇还好吗 -他没事 他走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How's Mickey? - He's ok. He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.86,0:43:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你想去找他吗 我们可以等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you wanna go and find him? We'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.04,0:43:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.03,0:43:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他该找更疼他的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He deserves better.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.58,0:43:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们出发吧 不停前行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Off we go, then. Always moving on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.51,0:43:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,下一站 拉克西科里科弗拉帕多里斯星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Next stop, Raxacoricofallapatorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.43,0:43:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这词可没多少机会说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now you don't often get to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.55,0:43:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就路过把她放进孵化场里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll just stop by and pop her in the hatchery.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.39,0:43:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,斯利辛人玛格丽特可以重新开始生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Margaret the Slitheen can live her life again.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.50,0:43:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,第二次机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A second chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.20,0:43:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那真是太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That'd be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.07,0:43:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉你件事 你现在是房客了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I gotta tell you something, you're a housemate,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.39,0:43:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,0)\pos(171.856,183.273)}{\fn黑体\fs28\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}下集预告
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.41,0:43:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你进入房子了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you're in the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.29,0:43:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这是不是很棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Isn't that brilliant?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.14,0:43:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到《智者为王》\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Welcome to The Weakest Link.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.35,0:43:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要给你一个全新形象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're giving you a brand-new image.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.69,0:43:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我穿的有什么不对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's wrong with what I'm wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.14,0:44:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事 -她被驱逐了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What was that? - She's been evicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.74,0:44:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不光是个游戏 -我需要找到博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This isn't just a game. - I need to find the Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.22,0:44:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他就在这里的哪个地方 他一直都在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's gonna be here somewhere! He's always here!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.20,0:44:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么其他事情发生了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's something else going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.63,0:44:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,有选手在游戏之外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have contestants outside the games.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.90,0:44:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,它们惧怕博士 -告诉我 它们是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs13}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They fear the Doctor. - Tell me, who are they?
